ID: CHG-TEN-REG-IMPL
NAME: Tenant Registration Domain Implementation (Phases 1-12)

DESCRIPTION
- Implemented the `tenant` domain registration capability as an object-based domain module with a cross-domain facade (`tenant_domain_api`), mounted API routes, DB-backed registration persistence, DB-backed tenant/org/user projection, Keycloak and OPA adapters (real-mode capable), replay-protected webhook verification, and SaaS onboarding integration.
- Added test coverage (unit + real-adapter integration) and a reusable Playwright e2e runner service for SaaS onboarding validation.

PRIMARY IMPLEMENTED AREAS

1) Tenant Domain Core
- `capabilities/tenant/factory.py`
- `capabilities/tenant/contracts/*`
- `capabilities/tenant/shared/*`
- `capabilities/tenant/caps/*`

2) Tenant Domain Persistence
- `capabilities/tenant/adapters/db/*`
- migration scaffolds and `0001_create_tenant_domain_tables.py`
- SQL store with registration/evidence persistence and webhook receipt replay protection
- core identity projection repository (`core.tenants`, `core.organizations`, `core.users`, `private.user_pii`)

3) IdP / Policy Integrations
- `capabilities/tenant/adapters/keycloak/*` (real admin mode support)
- `capabilities/tenant/adapters/opa/*` (real OPA HTTP decisions)
- OPA policy files under `capabilities/tenant/policies/tenant_registration/*.rego`
- local OPA compose wiring and policies under `/policies/*.rego`

4) API Runtime Integration
- `app/ingress/api/main.py` mounted tenant domain routes into real API runtime

5) SaaS Integration
- `ui-apps/service-gen-saas/lib/tenant-registration-client.ts`
- onboarding create/verify server actions wired to tenant API endpoints

6) E2E Test Infrastructure
- `ui-apps/service-gen-saas/playwright.config.ts`
- `ui-apps/service-gen-saas/tests/e2e/tenant-onboarding.spec.ts`
- `docker-compose.generated.yml` new `playwright-test` service
- `vendor/playwright-test/*` persistent runner assets/caches

