KNOWN LIMITATIONS / FOLLOW-UPS
- Tenant domain migration execution in a fully isolated production migration pipeline is scaffolded but not yet wired to a dedicated domain migration job in compose/k8s.
- Webhook validator is HMAC-based skeleton with realm/group checks; production mTLS and cloud secret rotation runbooks should be hardened further.
- Encryption uses Fernet utility with env key support; production KMS-backed key management/rotation remains a follow-up.

